      <title>韦丹塔将支付 9.32 亿美元股息以帮助母公司削减债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/vedanta-to-pay-932-million-in-dividend-to-help-parent-cut-debt</link>
